items.title: Supreme Court makes decision on gun law challenges in Delaware, Maryland
items.description: The Supreme Court on Monday declined to hear challenges to gun laws in Delaware and Maryland.

items.title: Newsom suspends CA environmental law to eliminate 'roadblocks' for wildfire victims rebuilding homes
items.description: Gov. Gavin Newsom lifted California's environmental review process for building laws for victims who lost their homes during the wildfire.
